ZH: 这本书详细介绍了人体各种脏器的功能。
EN: This book provides a detailed description of the functions of various internal organs in the human body.

ZH: 气管是一个重要的呼吸脏器。
EN: The trachea is an important respiratory organ.

ZH: 她患有心脏病，需要进行脏器移植手术。
EN: She has a heart condition and needs to undergo an organ transplant surgery.

ZH: 我们需要保护环境，以防止脏器曝露于毒素之中。
EN: We need to protect the environment to prevent organs from being exposed to toxins.

ZH: 血液在循环系统中起到输送营养至各个脏器的作用。
EN: Blood plays the role of transporting nutrients to various organs in the circulatory system.

ZH: 肝脏是人体内分泌和解毒的重要脏器。
EN: The liver is an important organ for endocrine and detoxification in the human body.

ZH: 胰脏分泌胰液，帮助消化系统消化食物。
EN: The pancreas secretes pancreatic juice to assist the digestive system in breaking down food.

ZH: 肺部是呼吸系统中的重要脏器。
EN: The lungs are important organs in the respiratory system.

ZH: 肾脏是人体内排泄废物的主要脏器。
EN: The kidneys are the main organs for excreting waste products in the human body.

ZH: 眼睛是感觉器官之一，是视觉信息的接收器和处理器。
EN: The eyes are one of the sensory organs responsible for receiving and processing visual information.

ZH: 骨髓是生产血细胞的关键脏器。
EN: Bone marrow is the crucial organ for producing blood cells.

ZH: 脑是人体的最重要的脏器之一，控制着各种生理和认知功能。
EN: The brain is one of the most vital organs in the human body, controlling various physiological and cognitive functions.

ZH: 这家医院专门进行脏器捐赠和移植手术。
EN: This hospital specializes in organ donation and transplant surgeries.

ZH: 骨骼是保护和支撑内部脏器的框架。
EN: The skeletal system provides a framework for protecting and supporting internal organs.

ZH: 我们要注意饮食，以保护肠道和其他消化脏器的健康。
EN: We should pay attention to our diet to protect the health of the intestines and other digestive organs.

ZH: 心脏是人体循环系统中的泵浦器官。
EN: The heart is the pumping organ in the circulatory system of the human body.

ZH: 运动可以提高器官和组织的血液循环。
EN: Exercise can improve blood circulation to organs and tissues.

ZH: 胃是消化系统中用于储存和消化食物的重要脏器。
EN: The stomach is an important organ in the digestive system for storing and digesting food.

ZH: 肺癌是一种影响肺部脏器的恶性肿瘤。
EN: Lung cancer is a malignant tumor that affects the organs in the lungs.

ZH: 有些疾病会导致脏器功能受损，需要接受特殊治疗。
EN: Some diseases can cause organ dysfunction, requiring specialized treatment.
